node.text:
Here is the after movie of STANCENATION JAPAN held at Kirara Expo Memorial Park in Yamaguchi.

This was our first time hosting the event in Yamaguchi! Thank you to everyone who participated!

Details will be available in upcoming issues of Geibunsha magazine as well as our site. You can also watch the live broadcast of the day's events on the “Stance JP Channel” on YouTube.

Event Date: November 8th 2020
Location: KIRARA EXPO MEMORIAL PARK (yamaguchi)
Vendors: 45
Entry Cars : 518 (1523 registered!)
Organizer: stancenation.com
Sponsored magazines:
Stance magazine,CUSTOM CAR,eS4,NostalgicSPEED,HACHIMARU HERO,VIP CAR mobile

node.text:
This message is for our Japan fans! The 2020 Hot Wheels Legend tour winner was @riley_rsmotorsport Pontiac, which will soon be sold as 1:64 DIE-CAST car in the near future.

The LEGENDS TOUR JAPAN is currently looking for a custom car to be immortalized into a #HotWheels die-cast. StanceNation founder @sn_elvis will be joining the StanceNation & Hot Wheels event in October 17th event as one of judges!

To enter, simply send in photos of your custom car from LEGEND TOUR JAPAN website or visit their Facebook page. You can also enter by visiting the StanceNation Japan
2021 AICHI and LEGENDS TOUR JAPAN!

#LegendsTourJapan #HotWheelsLegends #stancenation #stancenationjapan
